	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I got this mask tonight in my first time in Lower Guk.&nbsp;&nbsp;I got hooked up with a great group, some Runic Lore Guildmembers and some others.<br><br>I asked if we could check assassin, and we went slayed, and it dropped on fist kill, as well as the bag that reduces wieght off another mob.<br><br>They gladly let me take it (only one who could use it) and then when some of us died on the way out, we got 96% rezzes from Loops (thanks again).<br><br>The illusion doesnt work everywhere it is buggy.<br><br>Also, you have to turn it on by right-clicking on the mask.<br><br>$$$ DONT FORGET to turn it off when you go into a DE KOS area like FP or whatever.  Its great for sneaking around in those areas (I got it TO go to OT) but if you leave illusion on you will be bummed.  It looks great too.<br><br>I encourage every bard to go get this as soon as they hit about 30.  The effect looks *great* with SoL.<br><br>Enjoy, now its to OT for some serious exp.<br><br>Gileas Dreamsinger, MM server, Trusted Elves Guild, bard of the 30th string<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sat Feb  2 10:08:35 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
