alf the number of groups at any moment in any zone compared to blue servers), and that a two man group was camping the Assassin.  As soon as I arrived there, an assassin popped and got me the mask.  As I left the room, even though my hide and sneak buttons were still pressed, I had already lost my invis due to looting of the mask.  Good thing I noticed as I went down the ladder and conned a nearby ghoul.  It was a good thing that the zone was clear and that I was able to get out of the river past BR (bedroom) by taking off sneak.<br><br>Anyhow, after I arrived back in Everfrost, it came to me as a big shock and disappointment when I found that I could not use the mask as a level 5...<br><br>Well, there's my story.<br><br>BTW, does anyone know what level I can start using the mask?  Thanks.<br>&nbsp;<br>Dolus<br>Rallos Zek</td></tr>
